data.description: Welcome Home to 24031 Holleygate Ct in Villages of Spring Oaks! Incredible price on this beautifully renovated 1 story offers 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, open concept kitchen & family room. Over $25K renovation just completed August 2023- including new luxury vinyl flooring, interior wall paint & cabinet paint, granite countertops & backsplash in kitchen & both bathrooms, faucets & hardware, doors, AC tune-up, roof tune-up, exterior siding, shrubs trimmed & so much more! Refrigerator, washer & dryer remain with the property. *Brand New GE 4.8 Cu/Ft Freestanding Gas Range installed! New AC register has been ordered & will be installed in family room. * Refrigerator, Washer & Dryer included! Zoned to Spring ISD schools. Zone X- NO flooding! Excellent location to highways, shopping & dining. Priced BELOW appraisal value! Make your appointment today!
